item.title: [client] image with torches on it?
item.dc:creator: @WRX WRX`
item.description:
@WRX wrote:

[quote=“xx qwertyuiop xx, post:3, topic:251218”]Search for this code

class30_sub2_sub1_sub1 = new Class30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1(aClass44_1053, "logo", 0);
aClass15_1107.method237(0);
class30_sub2_sub1_sub1.method348(382 - class30_sub2_sub1_sub1.anInt1440 / 2 - 128, 16083, 18);

and comment the first and last lines out.

I don’t know about the torches. Is it black where they normally are, or does it show the background behind it?
Take a screenshot.[/quote]

Thanks, ALOT mate,

So now i only need torches, what i need basically, is an image which is a transparrent background with just the two torches on it, in the correct place, the torches without the fire on top.

Thanks alot guys.
